        "content": "<p>The first goal unfolds to:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">algebra.linear_map</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†¥</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†¥</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">range</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">algebra.linear_map</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†¥</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†¥</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">range</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
